          <text>I don't think I can do it. I was so excited, so sure I was close, that since I was out of that cage and had a lab and an infirmary that I could do anything. Anything! Cure the disease that's wiped out the vast majority of the world? Why not? I'll do it in a fucking high school lab! I'm a goddamn immunologist rockstar, sure! &lt;Parisa laughs ruefully and sighs.&gt;</text>
